title: EP.54: BRADY VS RODGERS, STEELERS STRUGGLE, MIAMI MAGIC, EAGLES SUPER BOWL CONTENTION, AND MUCH MORE!
description: With the eagles and dolphins looking strong who is the best undefeated team? Did the Packers deserve their win at Tampa Bay or was the missing Bucs WRs a valid excuse? Should the steelers move on and start Kenny Pickett? Tune in and find out more!
